text: Welcome to this stunning single-story home in the highly sought-after Paloma Lake community of Round Rock. With beautiful front landscaping & spacious 3-car garage, this home boasts incredible curb appeal. Step inside & you're greeted by a soaring entryway with elegant tile flooring, setting the tone for the thoughtful design & luxurious touches found throughout. The open & inviting layout features high ceilings & LVP flooring that flows seamlessly through the main living areas & bedrooms. The spacious living room, complete with gas log fireplace & elegant coffered ceilings with crown molding is the perfect place to gather. The heart of the home is the gourmet kitchen, boasting an extended island, 42-inch cabinetry, & SS appliances. Adjacent to the kitchen, the formal dining area leads to one of two covered patios offering a seamless indoor-outdoor living experience. The private primary suite is a true retreat, featuring spacious sitting area ideal for a home gym or reading nook. The spa-like ensuite bathroom includes a luxurious soaker tub, walk-in shower with bench, dual vanities with dressing counter, & expansive walk-in closet. Two additional bedrooms provide plenty of space, while the upstairs game room - complete with adjoining powder bath, offers versatile bonus space. A dedicated laundry room with built-in storage & folding counter ensures both convenience & efficiency. Step outside to the screened-in back patio, perfect for year-round enjoyment. Beyond the patio, the fully fenced backyard offers privacy, lush landscaping & plenty of space for outdoor activities. Additional highlights include a water softener with filtration, tankless water heater, full gutters, & built-in shelving throughout. Thoughtfully maintained, this home boasts a new roof & HVAC, radiant barrier, & fresh exterior paint. This luxury home offers access to scenic trails, parks & top-rated RRISD schools. Dont miss the chance to experience this premier property!
